items.summary: In `frontend/src/lib/eventIdLookup.ts`, update any entries for Dave Clarke's 9 events to match the corrected venue strings and dateTimes introduced in REQ-106. Specifically: (1) update the entry for the Vancouver event to reflect venue 'TBA (Industrial 236 Warehouse / Vantek Warehouse)' and dateTime '2026-03-06T22:00:00Z'; (2) update the entry for the Toronto event to reflect venue '821 Runnymede Rd (or 131 McCormack St)' and dateTime '2026-03-07T22:00:00Z'; (3) update the entry for the Brighton Concorde 2 event to dateTime '2026-05-15T22:00:00Z'; (4) update the entry for the Cardiff District Cardiff event to dateTime '2026-07-24T22:00:00Z'. Any existing entries whose composite keys no longer correspond to a live backend event ID (due to venue or dateTime changes) must be removed or updated so that the Add to Radar functionality continues to work correctly using the exact backend event IDs.
